for localization.

00:20:27.666 --> 00:20:30.926 A:middle
So, as you have text in your
application and you have buttons

00:20:30.926 --> 00:20:32.196 A:middle
with different lengths
of strings,

00:20:32.776 --> 00:20:35.156 A:middle
the buttons will
