00:20:35.416 --> 00:20:37.916 A:middle
to fit whatever string
your localization team puts

00:20:37.916 --> 00:20:39.686 A:middle
into the app.

00:20:39.946 --> 00:20:42.956 A:middle
So, going back to the specs from
