X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:23:58.756 --> 00:24:01.456 A:middle
And it basically just calls
drawViewHierarchyInRect

00:24:01.546 --> 00:24:03.996 A:middle
and makes the blur and applies
